COMMENT ON COLUMN PLAN_DETAILS.DETAIL_SEQ IS 'Part of the unique identifier of the plan detail record. Incremented within each case plan starting at 1.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN PLAN_DETAILS.GOAL_SUB_TYPE IS 'A code indicating the goal subtype. Ref Domain ( CASEPLAN_GOT - list filtered for parent code matching the selected goal type )';
COMMENT ON COLUMN PLAN_DETAILS.GOAL_TYPE IS 'A code indicating the type of goal. Ref Domain ( CASEPLAN_GOT )';
